    "text": "BP 180.0/120 — প্রি-এক্লাম্পসিয়া! বাম কাতে শোয়ান, ১০৮ কল করুন।",
    "tone": "emergency",
    "key": "e3a9ee7fa8f7b89814185b76cc76b7b9",
    "filename": "e3a9ee7fa8f7b89814185b76cc76b7b9.mp3",
    "bytes": 56256
  },
  {
    "text": "Home care. Routine follow-up per module schedule. Counsel on warning signs. Record visit on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7d7a933c91ca93ad8b8ebd6b9a63f92a",
    "filename": "7d7a933c91ca93ad8b8ebd6b9a63f92a.mp3",
    "bytes": 62208
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC within 24 h. Follow up in 2 days. Counsel on escalation signs. Record on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "77ec2ddcf63499d30e7e23068b8a372e",
    "filename": "77ec2ddcf63499d30e7e23068b8a372e.mp3",
    "bytes": 72960
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer FRU/SNCU/DH immediately (≤ 30–60 min). Call 108. Bengali action card displayed. Decision trace locked and stored. MDSR hook triggered if applicable.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c6a84f16225cdca30a85974c4bd7bff1",
    "filename": "c6a84f16225cdca30a85974c4bd7bff1.mp3",
    "bytes": 118080
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু বুকের দুধ খেতে পারছে না?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e0ed5ec512fab1bff7e62169e31b0b8e",
    "filename": "e0ed5ec512fab1bff7e62169e31b0b8e.mp3",
    "bytes": 21120
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately (≤ 30 min). Do not delay for any reason.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7c8e1fe2898b6f422b89b72bcce82916",
    "filename": "7c8e1fe2898b6f422b89b72bcce82916.mp3",
    "bytes": 72576
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর শরীরে জ্বর আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "317cd0817cfe548df0326ae6483b3083",
    "filename": "317cd0817cfe548df0326ae6483b3083.mp3",
    "bytes": 18624
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Any fever in a newborn is a danger sign.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "22747a0cd6a9b69be5a58366384c1b69",
    "filename": "22747a0cd6a9b69be5a58366384c1b69.mp3",
    "bytes": 57216
  },
  {
    "text": "শ্বাস-প্রশ্বাস দ্রুত বা কষ্টকর?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6813ac2eacf12cb0a96106dec41d7f4f",
    "filename": "6813ac2eacf12cb0a96106dec41d7f4f.mp3",
    "bytes": 23232
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Count RR — if ≥ 60/min = severe.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e8f4b43fbbceb2f40ec7d3a4009bcee7",
    "filename": "e8f4b43fbbceb2f40ec7d3a4009bcee7.mp3",
    "bytes": 79872
  },
  {
    "text": "নাভি লাল, ফোলা বা পুঁজ আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "03c8ec1d38eeb9d4a9f1bb084f4b31bb",
    "filename": "03c8ec1d38eeb9d4a9f1bb084f4b31bb.mp3",
    "bytes": 23424
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Omphalitis can progress to sepsis within hours.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "ded75d4391669bdf40e144b916cbf6e4",
    "filename": "ded75d4391669bdf40e144b916cbf6e4.mp3",
    "bytes": 42240
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু অনেক কম নড়ছে বা নিস্তেজ?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "04a565aad1201a069ab1f585286c341f",
    "filename": "04a565aad1201a069ab1f585286c341f.mp3",
    "bytes": 23616
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Lethargy = severe systemic illness.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b9a284444e6296dec5832a0300c86743",
    "filename": "b9a284444e6296dec5832a0300c86743.mp3",
    "bytes": 57408
  },
  {
    "text": "ত্বক হলুদ বা নীলাভ দেখাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "23d91a4a3213b5622a2fcb0414b57722",
    "filename": "23d91a4a3213b5622a2fcb0414b57722.mp3",
    "bytes": 21504
  },
  {
    "text": "Cyanosis or jaundice within 24 h = refer SNCU immediately. Jaundice day 2–14 without palm/sole involvement = refer PHC within 24 h for bilirubin check.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "70d6fd8a5d5cab98c974f4982f2beefc",
    "filename": "70d6fd8a5d5cab98c974f4982f2beefc.mp3",
    "bytes": 116736
  },
  {
    "text": "সব প্রশ্নের উত্তর না — কোনো বিপদচিহ্ন নেই?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "094adff23cdbd8c64b59d286eca81680",
    "filename": "094adff23cdbd8c64b59d286eca81680.mp3",
    "bytes": 30912
  },
  {
    "text": "HBNC home visit schedule: day 1, 3, 7, 14, 28. Counsel on exclusive breastfeeding, warmth, cord care, danger sign recognition.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "0c48a255d41f5012f5249300a990bc40",
    "filename": "0c48a255d41f5012f5249300a990bc40.mp3",
    "bytes": 104640
  },
  {
    "text": "পাঁচ দিনের বেশি জ্বর চলছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "fac9552325c385566fc8808807d91fb0",
    "filename": "fac9552325c385566fc8808807d91fb0.mp3",
    "bytes": 19584
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC/DH same day. Rule out malaria, typhoid, dengue. Do not give antipyretics and send home.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "bce14220f8fe0778ab355f1e359e0bfd",
    "filename": "bce14220f8fe0778ab355f1e359e0bfd.mp3",
    "bytes": 63360
  },
  {
    "text": "কাশি বা শ্বাসকষ্ট আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "18215733cc41dd7a72bd2484f5753472",
    "filename": "18215733cc41dd7a72bd2484f5753472.mp3",
    "bytes": 19200
  },
  {
    "text": "Count respiratory rate. RR ≥ 50 (2–12 m) or ≥ 40 (1–5 y) = pneumonia → PHC within 24 h. Chest indrawing or stridor = severe pneumonia → RED, refer FRU immediately.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "5851c030135ee28fe42dafb6849d14bf",
    "filename": "5851c030135ee28fe42dafb6849d14bf.mp3",
    "bytes": 190848
  },
  {
    "text": "ডায়রিয়া বা বারবার বমি হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "ce5c724924556b72d7a7d3e8b3e2b2b3",
    "filename": "ce5c724924556b72d7a7d3e8b3e2b2b3.mp3",
    "bytes": 21696
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess dehydration. No dehydration = GREEN (ORS at home). Some dehydration = YELLOW (ORS at PHC). Severe dehydration (sunken eyes, skin pinch slow, unable to drink) = RED, IV fluids at FRU.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "3107a611fd0580197c8ec065ee8d96ee",
    "filename": "3107a611fd0580197c8ec065ee8d96ee.mp3",
    "bytes": 154560
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু খেতে একদম অস্বীকার করছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "733b952514e12d4e4234879423bd06ac",
    "filename": "733b952514e12d4e4234879423bd06ac.mp3",
    "bytes": 22656
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess for illness cause. If associated with fever/diarrhoea = escalate to relevant rule. Isolated feeding refusal > 2 days = PHC referral within 24 h.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "fdd8f935852f11b57b11ec64f141f48d",
    "filename": "fdd8f935852f11b57b11ec64f141f48d.mp3",
    "bytes": 111168
  },
  {
    "text": "পানিশূন্যতার লক্ষণ (চোখ গর্তে, ঠোঁট শুকনো)?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "a0788f58ebbcff18948b8d586e80f2f7",
    "filename": "a0788f58ebbcff18948b8d586e80f2f7.mp3",
    "bytes": 34560
  },
  {
    "text": "Severe dehydration = RED. Start ORS immediately. Refer to FRU for IV fluids. Do not delay referral.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6b3f942e800d43ac6e300e828c10a49a",
    "filename": "6b3f942e800d43ac6e300e828c10a49a.mp3",
    "bytes": 75264
  },
  {
    "text": "ওজন বয়সের তুলনায় অনেক কম?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b72350b488ce29adb6e21e2a6ff71927",
    "filename": "b72350b488ce29adb6e21e2a6ff71927.mp3",
    "bytes": 20736
  },
  {
    "text": "Measure MUAC. MUAC < 11.5 cm or oedema = SAM → RED, refer NRC. MUAC 11.5–12.5 cm = MAM → YELLOW, refer ICDS/NRC for RUTF. MUAC > 12.5 cm = GREEN, counsel on feeding.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c205ec106b1fb3f1faf0471d5b519254",
    "filename": "c205ec106b1fb3f1faf0471d5b519254.mp3",
    "bytes": 212928
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু খাওয়া-দাওয়া একদম বন্ধ করে দিয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8e79cc3ac6d598398acb33eda31748e4",
    "filename": "8e79cc3ac6d598398acb33eda31748e4.mp3",
    "bytes": 26304
  },
  {
    "text": "Any feeding refusal in infant < 2 months = RED hard-stop. Refer FRU immediately.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "0a1e71557c34ea88af8e2cec50c907b6",
    "filename": "0a1e71557c34ea88af8e2cec50c907b6.mp3",
    "bytes": 60672
  },
  {
    "text": "তিন দিনের বেশি জ্বর চলছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "fa310dccd5cee68bd45dd867aa742cc8",
    "filename": "fa310dccd5cee68bd45dd867aa742cc8.mp3",
    "bytes": 19392
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC/FRU same day. Infants < 3 months with any fever = RED hard-stop.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "2b6acb84c8117e900ba53b3794ffc2d7",
    "filename": "2b6acb84c8117e900ba53b3794ffc2d7.mp3",
    "bytes": 53568
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess dehydration. Some dehydration = YELLOW, PHC within 24 h. Severe dehydration = RED, FRU for IV fluids.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "ea5197f7023ef0106ce2bbd7d4a2d011",
    "filename": "ea5197f7023ef0106ce2bbd7d4a2d011.mp3",
    "bytes": 87168
  },
  {
    "text": "শ্বাসকষ্ট বা বুকে শব্দ হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7dfb4ff0f8a9c51a63d28587c27958c6",
    "filename": "7dfb4ff0f8a9c51a63d28587c27958c6.mp3",
    "bytes": 23040
  },
  {
    "text": "Chest indrawing or stridor in infant = RED, refer FRU immediately. Fast breathing alone (RR ≥ 50) = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "d177a12bf629175c447e4f42c051c566",
    "filename": "d177a12bf629175c447e4f42c051c566.mp3",
    "bytes": 117696
  },
  {
    "text": "Severe dehydration in infant = RED. Start ORS immediately. Refer FRU for IV fluids.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c8b6d46c592feaf37854f99be6668946",
    "filename": "c8b6d46c592feaf37854f99be6668946.mp3",
    "bytes": 66240
  },
  {
    "text": "ওজন বাড়ছে না বা কমে যাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "d2c693f76e72c7d11afe049f28ead274",
    "filename": "d2c693f76e72c7d11afe049f28ead274.mp3",
    "bytes": 21696
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to ICDS/AWC for growth monitoring. If MUAC < 11.5 cm = RED, refer NRC. Counsel on complementary feeding after 6 months.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "acf5ff1bb5ef7452b84124f8b0d01a4c",
    "filename": "acf5ff1bb5ef7452b84124f8b0d01a4c.mp3",
    "bytes": 102144
  },
  {
    "text": "রক্তচাপ বেশি বা মাথা ব্যথা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "30be27baa3417223648d5ea3e0944cf9",
    "filename": "30be27baa3417223648d5ea3e0944cf9.mp3",
    "bytes": 25152
  },
  {
    "text": "Pre-eclampsia/eclampsia hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Do not give food/water. Lay on left side during transport.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7319ddad73b63dc27b6b38c32be61a05",
    "filename": "7319ddad73b63dc27b6b38c32be61a05.mp3",
    "bytes": 81408
  },
  {
    "text": "পা বা মুখ ফুলে যাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "fe2c7114c99d91037a480c1c169273d5",
    "filename": "fe2c7114c99d91037a480c1c169273d5.mp3",
    "bytes": 17472
  },
  {
    "text": "If oedema + headache + BP high = RED (pre-eclampsia). Isolated leg oedema = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h for BP check and urine protein.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "f02418c1f853ece69b7f9e3773fa64ca",
    "filename": "f02418c1f853ece69b7f9e3773fa64ca.mp3",
    "bytes": 101568
  },
  {
    "text": "রক্তপাত বা তীব্র পেট ব্যথা?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6716b3e5c769ecb58d08320e98671934",
    "filename": "6716b3e5c769ecb58d08320e98671934.mp3",
    "bytes": 21696
  },
  {
    "text": "APH hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Any bleeding after 20 weeks = emergency. Do not do vaginal examination.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "62b7d9c8ad2f05316f10c085c55000b7",
    "filename": "62b7d9c8ad2f05316f10c085c55000b7.mp3",
    "bytes": 80640
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর নড়াচড়া কমে গেছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "65f4d60819992e8d357d1c5c8e53fe44",
    "filename": "65f4d60819992e8d357d1c5c8e53fe44.mp3",
    "bytes": 19776
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to FRU/DH same day for fetal monitoring (CTG/Doppler). Absent fetal movement = emergency.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "522ed75d22d7487f26a837cf90cdf93c",
    "filename": "522ed75d22d7487f26a837cf90cdf93c.mp3",
    "bytes": 66240
  },
  {
    "text": "তিন মাসের বেশি ANC চেকআপ বাদ গেছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "4d5d52b0d232bc7c3b8972e37ab90d0c",
    "filename": "4d5d52b0d232bc7c3b8972e37ab90d0c.mp3",
    "bytes": 24000
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule ANC visit at PHC within 7 days. Check MCP card. Ensure TT, IFA, calcium supplementation are up to date. Flag for PMSMA if HRP.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "a9e938d0206ccaf60b0bec9962b1b0e2",
    "filename": "a9e938d0206ccaf60b0bec9962b1b0e2.mp3",
    "bytes": 111360
  },
  {
    "text": "চোখে ঝাপসা বা মাথা ঘোরা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "4d4f31e4dfa9246aee1bf76e2410ccda",
    "filename": "4d4f31e4dfa9246aee1bf76e2410ccda.mp3",
    "bytes": 23616
  },
  {
    "text": "Eclampsia prodrome hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Blurred vision + headache + oedema = imminent eclampsia.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "57e493cecbe3ab9ca2c45e9b022ef6a2",
    "filename": "57e493cecbe3ab9ca2c45e9b022ef6a2.mp3",
    "bytes": 70080
  },
  {
    "text": "Routine ANC follow-up. Ensure 4 ANC visits (8, 14, 28, 36 weeks). Counsel on IFA (180 tabs), calcium (360 tabs), TT2, diet, birth preparedness. Register on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "929aad3d64f8adf8b8335090569c1253",
    "filename": "929aad3d64f8adf8b8335090569c1253.mp3",
    "bytes": 149184
  },
  {
    "text": "অতিরিক্ত রক্তপাত বা দুর্গন্ধযুক্ত স্রাব?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "34993a1c8ecc6e370edc6eccce03a0b1",
    "filename": "34993a1c8ecc6e370edc6eccce03a0b1.mp3",
    "bytes": 28032
  },
  {
    "text": "PPH hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. If trained: bimanual uterine compression. Misoprostol 600 mcg sublingual if within ASHA scope (confirm at sign-off). Do not delay transport.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "545f30e3b63d3b9eddab6231751cf45b",
    "filename": "545f30e3b63d3b9eddab6231751cf45b.mp3",
    "bytes": 151296
  },
  {
    "text": "জ্বর বা ঠান্ডা লাগছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "3d5673c3c48a55dfa936f728b6e4a7c2",
    "filename": "3d5673c3c48a55dfa936f728b6e4a7c2.mp3",
    "bytes": 18240
  },
  {
    "text": "Puerperal sepsis risk. Fever + foul discharge = RED. Isolated fever day 1–2 = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h. Fever > 38°C after day 2 = RED.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1ea5ac0882cc2a82e556dc7383f8c6fc",
    "filename": "1ea5ac0882cc2a82e556dc7383f8c6fc.mp3",
    "bytes": 136704
  },
  {
    "text": "স্তনে ব্যথা, ফোলা বা লাল দাগ?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "71bbc2d8f130c2188b5ed66520bce266",
    "filename": "71bbc2d8f130c2188b5ed66520bce266.mp3",
    "bytes": 24000
  },
  {
    "text": "Mastitis: continue breastfeeding, warm compress, refer PHC within 24 h for antibiotics. If abscess (fluctuant swelling) = RED, refer FRU for I&D.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e1da94a02931380282f48631a8ea5ec0",
    "filename": "e1da94a02931380282f48631a8ea5ec0.mp3",
    "bytes": 112896
  },
  {
    "text": "পেটে তীব্র ব্যথা বা সেলাইয়ে সমস্যা?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "53171cf55ddbd2c6761889c62cee7486",
    "filename": "53171cf55ddbd2c6761889c62cee7486.mp3",
    "bytes": 24768
  },
  {
    "text": "Wound infection = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h. Wound dehiscence or severe pain = RED, refer FRU. Peritonitis signs (rigid abdomen, rebound tenderness) = RED hard-stop.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1bf43418308326091bf34dceec2b1cfa",
    "filename": "1bf43418308326091bf34dceec2b1cfa.mp3",
    "bytes": 129408
  },
  {
    "text": "প্রস্রাবে জ্বালা বা কষ্ট হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "f6ed2c2d4dda28598a52fe6e9535ea9f",
    "filename": "f6ed2c2d4dda28598a52fe6e9535ea9f.mp3",
    "bytes": 21696
  },
  {
    "text": "UTI: refer PHC within 24 h for urine culture and antibiotics. If fever + flank pain = pyelonephritis → RED, refer FRU.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "2bf27fb1a426e4c83ed706341ba8fd22",
    "filename": "2bf27fb1a426e4c83ed706341ba8fd22.mp3",
    "bytes": 101760
  },
  {
    "text": "খুব দুর্বল বা মাথা ঘোরা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "3cdff56f90472f1a41acbfc52500b744",
    "filename": "3cdff56f90472f1a41acbfc52500b744.mp3",
    "bytes": 22656
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess pallor (conjunctiva, palms). Severe pallor = anaemia → YELLOW, refer PHC for Hb check. Hb < 7 g/dL or fainting = RED, refer FRU for transfusion.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "915add093cdb122b57960629ed3bbf4e",
    "filename": "915add093cdb122b57960629ed3bbf4e.mp3",
    "bytes": 159936
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর বয়স কত মাস?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "044278f4adae725b26261bbd0d9abcf8",
    "filename": "044278f4adae725b26261bbd0d9abcf8.mp3",
    "bytes": 18240
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule catch-up at nearest session site within 7 days. BCG can be given up to 1 year. OPV/IPV/Pentavalent: give missed dose, continue schedule. Do not restart series.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "37a6142ccbe7ff71940f7ed8dbb15ff9",
    "filename": "37a6142ccbe7ff71940f7ed8dbb15ff9.mp3",
    "bytes": 101760
  },
  {
    "text": "কোন টিকা মিস হয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6bd41553a6e987fdea50c566a5563911",
    "filename": "6bd41553a6e987fdea50c566a5563911.mp3",
    "bytes": 16320
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule catch-up within 7 days. Measles-1 at 9 months, Vitamin A 1 lakh IU at 9 months. If > 12 months, give MMR instead of measles.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c151711acaa9da7d33c4896d2edf1643",
    "filename": "c151711acaa9da7d33c4896d2edf1643.mp3",
    "bytes": 101184
  },
  {
    "text": "কতদিন আগে টিকা দেওয়ার কথা ছিল?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "2eed1439ee55e053a00157134b5e4b14",
    "filename": "2eed1439ee55e053a00157134b5e4b14.mp3",
    "bytes": 21888
  },
  {
    "text": "Catch-up immunisation. Do not restart series. Give missed dose and continue from where left off. Refer to PHC for catch-up session. Flag on ANMOL for tracking.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "dc2ea65a036b4db4ac582208ddafc23a",
    "filename": "dc2ea65a036b4db4ac582208ddafc23a.mp3",
    "bytes": 100992
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর কি কোনো অসুস্থতা আছে এখন?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "92c4d2ccb211000879e9bd7c092da59d",
    "filename": "92c4d2ccb211000879e9bd7c092da59d.mp3",
    "bytes": 24000
  },
  {
    "text": "Mild illness (mild fever, cold) = vaccinate as scheduled. Moderate/severe illness = defer vaccination until recovered. Reschedule within 7 days of recovery. Do not miss opportunity for mild illness.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1d5e87f948803edaa94dc9bb7e713e92",
    "filename": "1d5e87f948803edaa94dc9bb7e713e92.mp3",
    "bytes": 132672
  },
  {
    "text": "১-৫ বছর বয়সী শিশুর বুস্টার ডোজ মিস হয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "08d4918c59d3b0a167d66343bca54dbc",
    "filename": "08d4918c59d3b0a167d66343bca54dbc.mp3",
    "bytes": 35328
  },
  {
    "text": "DPT booster at 16–24 months. OPV booster at 16–24 months. MMR at 15–18 months. Vitamin A 6-monthly up to 5 years. Schedule catch-up at next session.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "2d847dd9527613a192c503ef8a8fe4a3",
    "filename": "2d847dd9527613a192c503ef8a8fe4a3.mp3",
    "bytes": 129408
  },
  {
    "text": "অতিরিক্ত রক্তপাত হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8c079823961ce16534420443f6100380",
    "filename": "8c079823961ce16534420443f6100380.mp3",
    "bytes": 19200
  },
  {
    "text": "Hard-stop. Call 108 immediately. Refer FRU/DH ≤ 30 min. Apply uterine compression if postpartum. Do not leave patient alone.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "3346b2fb83209643a63a3c9b86650713",
    "filename": "3346b2fb83209643a63a3c9b86650713.mp3",
    "bytes": 96576
  },
  {
    "text": "খিঁচুনি বা অজ্ঞান হয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c36383af71bf37f8a89c6eb200c22da4",
    "filename": "c36383af71bf37f8a89c6eb200c22da4.mp3",
    "bytes": 18816
  },
  {
    "text": "Hard-stop. Lay on left side, protect airway. Call 108. Refer FRU/DH immediately. If eclampsia: MgSO4 loading dose if within ANM/MO scope. ASHA: do not delay transport.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "ea3654833e62d9caa76a4283b0e38f0c",
    "filename": "ea3654833e62d9caa76a4283b0e38f0c.mp3",
    "bytes": 116928
  },
  {
    "text": "শ্বাস নিতে খুব কষ্ট হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e23ad7977cad13e4405383c69e727523",
    "filename": "e23ad7977cad13e4405383c69e727523.mp3",
    "bytes": 20544
  },
  {
    "text": "Hard-stop. Call 108. Refer FRU/DH ≤ 30 min. Keep airway clear. If newborn: stimulate, clear airway, bag-mask if available.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "3f4a1cbbdc01e57476331e91837981da",
    "filename": "3f4a1cbbdc01e57476331e91837981da.mp3",
    "bytes": 100608
  },
  {
    "text": "রোগী সাড়া দিচ্ছে না বা জ্ঞান নেই?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c1803db7e2e5e98666bff67ea238e3c5",
    "filename": "c1803db7e2e5e98666bff67ea238e3c5.mp3",
    "bytes": 22272
  },
  {
    "text": "Hard-stop. Call 108 immediately. Check airway, breathing, circulation. Recovery position. Refer FRU/DH ≤ 30 min. MDSR audit trigger if death occurs.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "46f4171963f044973106b1c3071268e7",
    "filename": "46f4171963f044973106b1c3071268e7.mp3",
    "bytes": 117312
  },
  {
    "text": "উপরের যেকোনো একটি বিপদচিহ্ন আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "0234d5211429add608dc7e76d9adc119",
    "filename": "0234d5211429add608dc7e76d9adc119.mp3",
    "bytes": 24768
  },
  {
    "text": "System invariant: RED band locked. No GREEN or YELLOW answer can downgrade a fired RED. Re-sweep confirms RED on every state update.",
